data.text: The Department of Enterprise Services (DES) operates and maintains the Neal S. Blaisdell Center, the Tom Moffatt Waikīkī Shell, the Honolulu Zoo and six municipal golf courses. DES also coordinates the preparation, administration and enforcement of City and County of Honolulu concession contracts. DES is the only city department with an operating budget primarily funded by revenues generated from public events and activities.
